            "content_html": "<pre>負責項目 : layout、前後端切版<br>製作期間 : 10天 (July.2021)<br>使用工具 : sketch、VUE、html、css<br><br>🔗 <a href=\"https://eschool.sesamevillage.arks.tw/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">https://eschool.sesamevillage.arks.tw/</a></pre>\n<blockquote>\n<p>「Sesame Street English —芝蔴街美語教材」結合芝蔴街廣受全世界兒童喜愛的布偶、教育專家的心血、電腦動畫、高科技電子產品、豐富的教學經驗為一體。</p>\n<p>目標用戶廣為兒童、家長及老師所使用，藉由芝蔴街角色融入設計，使整體風格更為俏皮活潑，並且在介面上注重易於閱讀與操作的設計方式。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<figure class=\"post__image\" ><figure class=\"post__image\"><img loading=\"lazy\"  src=\"https://enidleeee.github.io/portfolio/media/posts/1/sesamevillag6-3.png\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" srcset=\"https://enidleeee.github.io/portfolio/media/posts/1/responsive/sesamevillag6-3-xs.png 300w ,https://enidleeee.github.io/portfolio/media/posts/1/responsive/sesamevillag6-3-sm.png 480w ,https://enidleeee.github.io/portfolio/media/posts/1/responsive/sesamevillag6-3-md.png 768w ,https://enidleeee.github.io/portfolio/media/posts/1/responsive/sesamevillag6-3-lg.png 1024w\"  alt=\"\" width=\"1280\" height=\"981\"></figure>\n<figcaption >入口頁 : 分為總部、老師、學生登入導引</figcaption>\n</figure>\n<figure class=\"post__image\" ><figure class=\"post__image\"><img loading=\"lazy\"  src=\"https://enidleeee.github.io/portfolio/media/posts/1/Group-63-2.png\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" srcset=\"https://enidleeee.github.io/portfolio/media/posts/1/responsive/Group-63-2-xs.png 300w ,https://enidleeee.github.io/portfolio/media/posts/1/responsive/Group-63-2-sm.png 480w ,https://enidleeee.github.io/portfolio/media/posts/1/responsive/Group-63-2-md.png 768w ,https://enidleeee.github.io/portfolio/media/posts/1/responsive/Group-63-2-lg.png 1024w\"  alt=\"\" width=\"1280\" height=\"596\"></figure>\n<figcaption >總部-SITEMAP</figcaption>\n</figure>\n<p> </p>\n<figure class=\"post__image\" ><figure class=\"post__image\"><img loading=\"lazy\"  src=\"https://enidleeee.github.io/portfolio/media/posts/1/Group-64-2.png\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" srcset=\"https://enidleeee.github.io/portfolio/media/posts/1/responsive/Group-64-2-xs.png 300w ,https://enidleeee.github.io/portfolio/media/posts/1/responsive/Group-64-2-sm.png 480w ,https://enidleeee.github.io/portfolio/media/posts/1/responsive/Group-64-2-md.png 768w ,https://enidleeee.github.io/portfolio/media/posts/1/responsive/Group-64-2-lg.png 1024w\"  alt=\"\" width=\"1280\" height=\"597\"></figure>\n<figcaption >老師端-SITEMAP</figcaption>\n</figure>\n<figure class=\"post__image\"><img loading=\"lazy\"  src=\"https://enidleeee.github.io/portfolio/media/posts/1/sesamevillage4-3.png\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" srcset=\"https://enidleeee.github.io/portfolio/media/posts/1/responsive/sesamevillage4-3-xs.png 300w ,https://enidleeee.github.io/portfolio/media/posts/1/responsive/sesamevillage4-3-sm.png 480w ,https://enidleeee.github.io/portfolio/media/posts/1/responsive/sesamevillage4-3-md.png 768w ,https://enidleeee.github.io/portfolio/media/posts/1/responsive/sesamevillage4-3-lg.png 1024w\"  alt=\"\" width=\"1280\" height=\"882\"></figure>\n<figure class=\"post__image\"><img loading=\"lazy\"  src=\"https://enidleeee.github.io/portfolio/media/posts/1/sesamevillage2-3.png\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" srcset=\"https://enidleeee.github.io/portfolio/media/posts/1/responsive/sesamevillage2-3-xs.png 300w ,https://enidleeee.github.io/portfolio/media/posts/1/responsive/sesamevillage2-3-sm.png 480w ,https://enidleeee.github.io/portfolio/media/posts/1/responsive/sesamevillage2-3-md.png 768w ,https://enidleeee.github.io/portfolio/media/posts/1/responsive/sesamevillage2-3-lg.png 1024w\"  alt=\"\" width=\"1280\" height=\"775\"></figure>\n<figure class=\"post__image\"><img loading=\"lazy\"  src=\"https://enidleeee.github.io/portfolio/media/posts/1/Frame-3.png\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" srcset=\"https://enidleeee.github.io/portfolio/media/posts/1/responsive/Frame-3-xs.png 300w ,https://enidleeee.github.io/portfolio/media/posts/1/responsive/Frame-3-sm.png 480w ,https://enidleeee.github.io/portfolio/media/posts/1/responsive/Frame-3-md.png 768w ,https://enidleeee.github.io/portfolio/media/posts/1/responsive/Frame-3-lg.png 1024w\"  alt=\"\" width=\"1280\" height=\"1153\"></figure>\n<figure class=\"post__image\" ><figure class=\"post__image\"><img loading=\"lazy\"  src=\"https://enidleeee.github.io/portfolio/media/posts/1/Group-65-2.png\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" srcset=\"https://enidleeee.github.io/portfolio/media/posts/1/responsive/Group-65-2-xs.png 300w ,https://enidleeee.github.io/portfolio/media/posts/1/responsive/Group-65-2-sm.png 480w ,https://enidleeee.github.io/portfolio/media/posts/1/responsive/Group-65-2-md.png 768w ,https://enidleeee.github.io/portfolio/media/posts/1/responsive/Group-65-2-lg.png 1024w\"  alt=\"\" width=\"1280\" height=\"597\"></figure>\n<figcaption >老師端-SITEMAP</figcaption>\n</figure>\n<figure class=\"post__image\"><img loading=\"lazy\"  src=\"https://enidleeee.github.io/portfolio/media/posts/1/sesamevillage5.png\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" srcset=\"https://enidleeee.github.io/portfolio/media/posts/1/responsive/sesamevillage5-xs.png 300w ,https://enidleeee.github.io/portfolio/media/posts/1/responsive/sesamevillage5-sm.png 480w ,https://enidleeee.github.io/portfolio/media/posts/1/responsive/sesamevillage5-md.png 768w ,https://enidleeee.github.io/portfolio/media/posts/1/responsive/sesamevillage5-lg.png 1024w\"  alt=\"\" width=\"1280\" height=\"781\"></figure><br><br></p>\n<p><strong><span style=\"color: #236fa1;\">#web  #education</span></strong></p>",
